description:
Meet the latest addition to Active Duty: Julian!

The strapping fella is brand new in the War Chest tonight, and I'm glad I've been able to convince him to step in front of the camera. I've been working on getting him to film a scene for a while now, convincing him to take the plunge, and as you'll see, we've succeeded!

Director Kaden is manning this scene, and he starts by chatting up Julian about his experience so far with us. 'It's been interesting... fun,' Julian says, adding that he's been having a 'good time.' Aw, Julian, you know all the right things to say!

Kaden asks if this is his first time in front of the camera, and he says yes... but then offers an interesting story of how a guy paid him $1,000 to have sex with his wife. (You'll have to watch to hear the whole thing -- it's a doozy.)

Julian stands 5'10' and weighs about 175 lbs. and has brown hair and brown eyes. He says he likes to work out -- and you can tell. He's also got an adorable smile and a beautiful baby face. Julian says he used to be 'fat,' but then worked like a dog to get the weight off, barely eating. He says he loves partying -- and talks about a crazy night where he had just consumed a bit too much.

After the chat, it's time to get the party started. Julian's got a pretty buff body, and he shows it all off in this scene. I think you're gonna enjoy Julian -- and you just might see more of him in the near future!
title: Julian - Solo
